## Additional Terms for Educational Content

This project contains educational materials that are intended to help developers
learn system design concepts. The following additional terms apply:

### Educational Use
- Content may be used for educational purposes without restriction
- Attribution is appreciated but not required for educational use
- Derivative educational works are encouraged and welcomed

### Commercial Use
- Commercial use of the educational content is permitted under the MIT license
- If you create paid courses or materials based on this content, we'd appreciate
  a mention or link back to this repository
- Revenue sharing with contributors is encouraged for commercial derivatives

### Community Contributions
- All contributors retain their individual copyrights to their contributions
- By contributing, you grant the project a license to use your contribution
  under the terms of this MIT license
- You may also license your contributions under additional terms if desired

